{"tid":938272,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓國TL】向女友施暴力被判罰款 吸毒罪成判緩刑","createTime":"2018-12-12T07:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T02:16:09.000Z","uid":142787,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"556badf8a9b2cb0ad8ae4960c61a73d9cbac1c47","tid":938272,"uid":142787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181212/large/1544589608_cd71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181212%2Flarge%2F1544589608_cd71.jpg&h=e5a64741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創作韓國人氣綜藝節目《PRODUCE 101》主題曲《Pick Me》嘅音樂人Maximite，5月時被爆涉嫌吸大麻而被調查，之後再被爆因對女友施暴力而被不拘留立案調查。<br />\n<br />\nMaximite對女友施暴力一案，日前於一審中被判處罰款300萬韓圜（約21,000港元）。另外，Maximite因吸毒而被判處有期徒刑兩年半，緩刑三年，同時需從事80個小時嘅社會服務、接受40個小時嘅藥物治療講課及罰款25.3萬韓圜（約1,770港元）。"},{"pid":"f30e4db33ad6eec9b4e01dc3c11365fea19b7929","tid":938272,"uid":172507,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"What's up party people~"},{"pid":"a173a93c2d2174a55eb25f6b8045c6508bd5ab29","tid":938272,"uid":171594,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"TL邊有女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743bf2bd8a0f2097c4363c09e2235522474dd874","tid":938272,"uid":93078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:10:18.000Z","msg":"罰咗少錢"},{"pid":"2bc7fb3d3fddcfac874fdc7da4b85d8f76e6337d","tid":938272,"uid":93078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"743bf2bd8a0f2097c4363c09e2235522474dd874","tid":938272,"uid":93078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:10:18.000Z","msg":"罰咗少錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:10:31.000Z","msg":"罰咁少錢"},{"pid":"1ac71be4455ba95110b6c8eecdd